<!--pages/medicineAsk/medicineAsk.wxml-->

<view class='page' style="padding-top:{{ztlH2}}px">

  <view class='fHead' style="padding-top:{{ztlH}}px">
    <navigator open-type="navigateBack">
      <image src='../../frame/icon-37.png'></image>
    </navigator>
    <text>用药咨询</text>
  </view>

  <swiper indicator-dots="{{indicatorDots}}"
    autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" duration="{{duration}}">
    <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}">
      <swiper-item>
        <image src="{{item}}" class="slide-image" mode='widthFix'/>
      </swiper-item>
    </block>
  </swiper>

  <view class='info'>
    <text class='i1'>服务信息</text>
    <text class='i2'>患者提交病例及用药方案后:</text>
    <view class='i3'>
      <text>24小时内获得会由香港医生与患者联系，进行在线预诊时内获得会由香港医生</text>
      <text>凭处方可从印度任一正规药房购买相应药品</text>
      <text>患者或家属赴香港诊所就医、购药</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='process'>
    <text class='i1'>服务流程</text>
    <view class='list'>
      <view class='item'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-8.png'></image>
        <view></view>
        <text>上传病例</text>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-9.png'></image>
        <view></view>
        <text>在线咨询</text>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-10.png'></image>
        <view></view>
        <text>预约赴港</text>
      </view>
      <view class='item'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-11.png'></image>
        <view></view>
        <text>就医购药</text>
      </view>
    </view>


  </view>

  <view class='doctor'>
    <text class='i1'>提供服务的医生</text>
    <scroll-view scroll-x>
      <view class='list'>
        <view class='item'>
          <view class='hd'>
            <text style='background-image:url(../../frame/icon-33.png)'>6</text>
            <image src='../../images/img-15.jpg'></image>
          </view>
          <view class='bd'>
            <text class='o1'>MD Anderson Lucis</text>
            <text class='o2'>Appollo Hospital</text>
            <text class='o3'>肿瘤主任医生</text>
          </view>
          <button>详细</button>
        </view>

        <view class='item'>
          <view class='hd'>
            <text style='background-image:url(../../frame/icon-33.png)'>6</text>
            <image src='../../images/img-15.jpg'></image>
          </view>
          <view class='bd'>
            <text class='o1'>MD Anderson Lucis</text>
            <text class='o2'>Appollo Hospital</text>
            <text class='o3'>肿瘤主任医生</text>
          </view>
          <button>详细</button>
        </view>

        <view class='item'>
          <view class='hd'>
            <text style='background-image:url(../../frame/icon-33.png)'>6</text>
            <image src='../../images/img-15.jpg'></image>
          </view>
          <view class='bd'>
            <text class='o1'>MD Anderson Lucis</text>
            <text class='o2'>Appollo Hospital</text>
            <text class='o3'>肿瘤主任医生</text>
          </view>
          <button>详细</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class='question'>
    <text class='i1'>常见问题</text>
    <view class='item'>
      <view class='i2'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-12.png'></image>
        <text>获取处方后如何购药？</text>
      </view>
      <view class='i3'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-13.png'></image>
        <text>医生开具印度处方后，患者可凭此处方自行于印度各正规药房进行购买，目前印度各大连锁药房基本都提供邮购服务，一般邮寄到中国的时效为10-15天</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='item'>
      <view class='i2'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-12.png'></image>
        <text>服务费用中是否包含药品费用？</text>
      </view>
      <view class='i3'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-13.png'></image>
        <text>本服务为用药咨询服务，不提供药品销售！药品费用由药房收取，并负责物流相关事务。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='item'>
      <view class='i2'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-12.png'></image>
        <text>如何确保医生资质和处方合法性？</text>
      </view>
      <view class='i3'>
        <image src='../../frame/icon-13.png'></image>
        <text>所有提供服务的医生都为印度正式注册医生，印度的法律允许医生远程问诊开具合法处方，所有处方皆有患者信息及医生签名，无法进行伪造</text>
      </view>
    </view>

  </view>

  <view class='btn'>
    <navigator class='i1'>
      <image src='../../frame/icon-14.png'></image>
      <text>在线咨询</text>
    </navigator>
     <view class="i2" bindtap="specialistScheme">
      <image src='../../frame/icon-15.png'></image>
      <text>获取用药指导及处方</text>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>